Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}乙坂有宇 15岁 男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}负责医生 小池医师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}点滴警报一览 以数字点灭表示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}滴落传感器安装不良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}滴落无法检测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}滴落速率不均
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}滴落速率不均
