Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然痛咯 手术才刚过去两天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我动也不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 去问医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
